<plot>When Lt Bear retires from active duty, he goes to look up some of his former subordinates in the secret hope of finding employment. However, he is horrified to see the paths their individual lives have taken--one is a gambler, another is a hippie and a third is obsessed with emigrating from Korea for a new life in another country. Through his advice and acts of kindness, he attempts to turn their lives around.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?219398</url></doc>
